OL,6,FLive music venues and theatres in the
OL,7,FSouth West are facing a funding
OL,8,Fcrisis, according to those who run
OL,9,Fthem.JDespite efforts to redistribute
OL,10,Fmoney around the country, figures show
OL,11,Fthe region remains well behind other
OL,12,Fareas in terms of arts investment and
OL,13,Fvenues are closing as a result.
OL,14,FTheatre directors and gig promoters
OL,15,Fare calling on the government and
OL,16,Flocal councils to do more, warning it
OL,17,Fis becoming difficult for performers
OL,18,Fto make a living and attract audiences.
