OL,6,FEzmay Grace is a singer-songwriter
OL,7,Fbased in north . She believes
OL,8,Fcreativity is vital for our wellbeing.
OL,9,FShe said: "I think it's incredibly
OL,10,Fimportant that we fund the arts well.
OL,11,FI would love to see what people
OL,12,Fthought of a world without music,
OL,13,Fwithout television, without museums
OL,14,Fand art. I think that we'd all be
OL,15,Fabsolutely miserable.
OL,17,F"Music can never disappear. The arts
OL,18,Fcan never disappear. It's
OL,19,Fentertainment. It's what keeps people
OL,20,Fhappy. It's what keeps people going."
