OL,6,FRegional arts venues, like the , are
OL,7,Fstruggling. Laura Horton, who recently
OL,8,Ftook over as artistic consultant,
OL,9,Fsaid: "It's really hard.
OL,11,F"There's very little funding out
OL,12,Fthere. People are struggling to make
OL,13,Fwork, and I feel like there's a lot of
OL,14,Fmistrust in the arts sometimes, and
OL,15,Fit's the first thing to go.
OL,17,F"There are a few theatres recently
OL,18,Fthat have fully lost their funding
OL,19,Ffrom their council, and it would be
OL,20,Fheartbreaking to see that happening
OL,21,Fhere.
